# Test Results Directory

Store completed test results here:

```
results/
├── 2024-11-17/
│   ├── test-results-complete.md
│   ├── issues-found.md
│   ├── performance-metrics.csv
│   └── sign-off.pdf
├── 2024-11-18/
│   └── ...
```

## What to Store

- Completed TEST_RESULTS_TEMPLATE.md
- Issue reports
- Performance metrics
- Sign-off documents
- Test summary reports
- Recommendations documents

## Naming Convention

`[type]-[date].[ext]`

Examples:
- `test-results-complete-2024-11-17.md`
- `issues-critical-2024-11-17.md`
- `performance-metrics-2024-11-17.csv`
- `sign-off-2024-11-17.pdf`
